{"tid":611613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又冧網】中國聯通疑又死機 客戶訴苦不能上網打電話如陷孤島","createTime":"2018-03-31T07:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T07:53:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7b528277c1b10e66c21d700aaa4fc4b5565028","tid":611613,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180331/large/1522480225_5470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180331%2Flarge%2F1522480225_5470.jpg&h=99bd585a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 電訊商中國聯通懷疑又「死機」？！繼上月27日曾出現故障令大量客戶無法使用電話及上網服務後，中國聯通今午又疑再出問題，大量香港的中國聯通客戶在網上包括中聯通官方fb留言訴苦指通訊失靈，包括「上唔到網」、「打唔到電話」，有顧客質疑「有冇壞得咁密啊？」有事主親身到門市求助，但無果，並指已出現排隊的人龍；有人怒斥中國聯通服務差，指不足兩個月內兩度發生嚴重故障實難以接受，要求電訊商「回水」或「解約」。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者正致電中國聯通了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，記者到荃灣南豐廣場的中國聯通門市了解，有顧客正向職員投訴：「今朝打極都打唔到電話呀！」職員透露，電話話音服務故障，但上網服務如常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180331/58018037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58018037&d=NGHX1sD0FsocOWVjFLgZz54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=862cc895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58018037&h=78de36ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180331/58018037</a>"}]}